出退伍軍人病疾病警告<br />\n<br />\nThe paper said that as the source of the outbreak had not been identified, anyone visiting or living in Dubai could still be at risk of exposure to the Legionella bacteria.<br />\n<br />\n並未找出源頭<br />\n<br />\nLegionnaires' disease is a type of pneumonia that usually starts with flu-like symptoms, including fever, tiredness, headache, and muscle pains. These are followed by a dry cough and breathing difficulties, which may progress to a severe pneumonia. <br />\n<br />\n一開始會有好似流感嘅病徵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.khaleejtimes.com/nation/dubai/flying-to-dubai-legionnaires-disease-warning-issued\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.khaleejtimes.com%2Fnation%2Fdubai%2Fflying-to-dubai-legionnaires-disease-warning-issued&d=v7nfW4n%2FZMB2RpSCwKRmzjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=fb6ca2d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.khaleejtimes.com/nation/dubai/flying-to-dubai-legionnaires-disease-warning-issued</a>"},{"pid":"121cbd77a850da24ff4df9dd840ae64ddeb9ed4c","tid":807664,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270fdeb877887dffae6c4d1f022dbc5dc00db6bd","tid":807664,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T00:33:56.000Z","msg":"Google mecca flu 係搵唔到咩流感爆發嘅新聞<br />\n但有講大規模朝聖會增加流感/呼吸道疾病爆發嘅風險"},{"pid":"9614e1946151bdaf9fd14fee5ad1e34d5e9fd077","tid":807664,"uid":17266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c004ba8bec7eab6c1c01cb7d64176311f713144e","tid":807664,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b97f22928617dc0b10aa61be426aa455be29e3b4","tid":807664,"uid":2054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1-oTyRnd2y0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1-oTyRnd2y0&d=v7nfW4n%2FZMB2RpSCwKRmzjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=13c